{
  "stem": "3949.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My name is Elizabeth Egri Deutsch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "E-G-R-I, my maiden name, and my married name is D-E-U-T-S-C-H.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hebrew names, they used to call me Esther.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's August 23, 1927.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "67.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I came from-- I was born in Bodrogkeresztur in Hungary, and that was in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's B-O-D-R-O-G-K-E-R-E-S-Z-T-U-R.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a long name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was very interesting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a young child growing up in a village, I lived with my parents and three brothers-- older brothers-- and one older sister.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I also had my grandparents, and aunts, and uncles, and cousins.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were a big family and a very close knit family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In our little village, everybody was very close to each other.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was really like a big family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Population was about 3,500 people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And among the people, we were about 600 Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had two synagogues.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had lots of stores, small stores.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, my grandparents had one of them, a grocery store.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother's parents, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we were living in Hungary, and my father was living, actually, in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In home in Europe, they used to have [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't know exactly the story how they met, but my father wind up in Hungary and married my mother.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so it was a quiet, interesting place to live in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] As a child growing up, it was-- you know, with older-- mostly the Jewish people, they lived on main street.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But houses were scattered around the valleys and the hills.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So also we had Bodrog, and people used to come and bathe there in the summertime, like a summer place, from other town around.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had a post office.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had a townhouse.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had a police station.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We didn't have inside plumbing.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
